  <class_name>AddRemoveOrReplaceWindows</class_name>
  <display_name>Add Remove Or Replace Windows</display_name>
  <description>Before running this measure run surface matching and remove window overhangs. Adds ribbon windows to exterior walls on the selected facade if none exist. Removes all windows on the selected facade. Replaces all windows on the selected facade with ribbon windows.</description>
  <modeler_description>Loops through exterior surfaces on the selected facade and either adds, removes, or replaces a subsurface.</modeler_description>
